  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc7\u0baf\u0bc7 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fatal accident in Batticaloa - Two brothers die on the spot",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two brothers from the same family (a brother and a younger brother) who were traveling on a motorcycle died on the spot in a vehicle accident that took place in Tannamunya, Batticaloa on Tuesday afternoon (26).",
        "The deceased are two brothers from Saturukondan village. It is also known that the accident took place when a motorcycle collided with a tipper type vehicle.",
        "It is worth noting that the Batticaloa Police have conducted further investigations into the accident."
      ],
